<li class='cover' id='bookCover_53458056'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53458056-monsters"><img alt="Monsters" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1605025936l/53458056._SX98_.jpg" />
