<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6998854454459918867"><strong>Richard Powers</strong> has published thirteen novels. He is a MacArthur Fellow and received the National Book Award. His most recent book, <em>The Overstory</em>, won the Pulitzer Prize in Fiction. He lives in the Great Smoky Mountains.<br/><br/> <i>Librarian note: There is more than one author with this name in the Goodreads database. </i></span>

</div>
